4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists without prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Students will build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, while also mastering topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop